# `java` arguments for the `build` command  | -*- coding: us-ascii; mode: conf-javaprop; -*-
#
# This is a `java` command-line argument file.  It is a referent of `./build`.  For syntax and so forth:
# `https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/14/docs/specs/man/java.html#java-command-line-argument-files`.

    -enableassertions:building...
   --source 14 # Requesting source launch of a file (`build`) that lacks a `.java` extension.
       # https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/14/docs/specs/man/java.html#using-source-file-mode-to-launch-single-file-source-code-programs
    -XX:+ShowCodeDetailsInExceptionMessages # https://openjdk.java.net/jeps/358


